To: All Employees of DefenseTech
From: Jon Snow, Head of Weapons Development
Subject: Excitement over DOD Weapons Contract

Dear All,

I am thrilled to announce that we have been awarded a new weapons contract with the DOD. As many of you know, this has been a long time coming and we could not be more excited about the opportunities it presents for our company. The new contract will allow us to push the boundaries of what we have been able to achieve in terms of developing cutting-edge technology and advanced weaponry.

Our team has worked incredibly hard to secure this contract and I want to thank each and every one of you for your hard work and dedication. It is thanks to your commitment to excellence that we are able to continue to grow and innovate as a company.

I look forward to working with you all as we embark on this exciting new chapter in the history of Stark Industries.

Sincerely,
Jon Snow
